sentences.english: The pumping source is a switch type and inverse excitation model in small size but it has high efficiency.
sentences.chinese: 泵浦系統是小型高效率開關型反激式脈衝泵浦源。

sentences.english: A laser-diode-pumped Nd:FAP laser oscillator is reported in this paper.
sentences.chinese: 報道激光二極管泵浦的摻釹氟磷酸鈣固體激光器。

sentences.english: The behaviour of passively Q-switched solid-state lasers containing intracavity optical parametric oscillators(OPOs) is described in detail.
sentences.chinese: 理論分析了被動調Q固體激光泵浦的光參量振盪器。

sentences.english: Some botanists hypothesized that the living cells of plants acted as pumps.
sentences.chinese: 有些植物學家假設植物活細胞作爲泵浦。

sentences.english: Engineers pumped massive amounts of water under high pressure down into hot rock.
sentences.chinese: 工程師泵浦高壓下分解成熱巖大量的水。

sentences.english: We also discuss the effect of the coherent pumping on the laser line width.
sentences.chinese: 同時討論了相干泵浦對激光線寬的影響。

sentences.english: In this paper, a high repetition-rate Ti:sapphire laser pumped by flashlamp is reported.
sentences.chinese: 報道了一臺高重複率閃光燈泵浦的摻鈦寶石激光器。

sentences.english: The higher the pumping power, the more are the pairs of the vector soliton bunch.
sentences.chinese: 泵浦功率越高，裂變出來的矢量孤子簇對數越多。

sentences.english: So far many side-pumping methods have been presented and realized.
sentences.chinese: 目前已經提出並且實現了多種側面泵浦耦合技術。

sentences.english: The cost of a blending pump would more closely match that of an E85 pump.
sentences.chinese: 燃料混合泵的成本將會更接近於E85泵浦的成本。

sentences.english: With pump feed and continuous mill, it also applies to small lot manufacture.
sentences.chinese: 泵浦輸送，連續式研磨，所以也可以進行小批量生產。
